{"tid":2491181,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"UST南亞仔(#21545)炒車搞批鬥扮大台帶風向整合","createTime":"2021-04-16T06:25:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T06:54:04.000Z","uid":73381,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"45ead9837ca930b76aff9e3e746fbf204a08570f","tid":2491181,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T06:25:37.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>帶風向老屈加泰奶共</strong></span><br />\n（個人意見）我自己唔會去加泰集會 因為佢哋撐共<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1670675\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1670675</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>柒咗就道歉想洗底</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXqcvRExc1aEjxuL8wefh2maksi2vb1PrMwkZdDWFrjLb?filename=x4TnBxa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx4TnBxa.jpg&h=bbe2542a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>扮大台指指點點</strong></span><br />\n（溫馨提示）一陣維吾爾集會 盡量唔好有連豬連狗出現<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eFRFOS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eFRFOS</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>點知原來係唔識又要扮識</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSRf1YP7AeyTLWooZQq5j2FYdfg3Dxm5CFNrqjo8ErCJL?filename=tBS7ND7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtBS7ND7.jpg&h=bd1d4579&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>扮大台</strong></span><br />\n我正式宣布黃色經濟圈快將收皮<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fogpxS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fogpxS</a><br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><br />\n比人屌柒就道歉扮中文唔好 屌你老味你得1/8南亞血統咋中文唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTc3U8SQeKCmAP4YYr1igoQYSmYpqsPkwGLMpG2bNZqCg?filename=zvEYUma.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzvEYUma.jpg